{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>資深藝人施明上月病逝，今日（23日）將於大圍寶福紀念館設靈。李泳漢與李家鼎加李泳豪近幾日不停在網上隔互空數，李家鼎更慘成淚水向傳媒哭訴，聞者心酸。今日李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂，除了豪妻被拒絕入靈堂內，李家鼎明顯神情憔悴，早前有傳媒報道他暴瘦至120磅，後變成紙片人，非常令人擔心。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659390222602240847951.jpeg/jmRQt99mZKEhnpJCgvI0lZCbt6ylw-AOHi2Ljygti48\" alt=\"李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659404227907584756481.jpeg/ze93QU8IuyqkYAzzSFav_xqlR9pIBGh49iXP0cAlz9E\" alt=\"李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659401581170688610987.jpeg/SYwVuG2WhNbkdbCzEh8GP3V7iDERl1W1aoi921yIvds\" alt=\"李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659398984765440746380.jpeg/qlbacbHdageIw3GGq6eFj1z1oZYXg9W54uA2C9TgNgs\" alt=\"李家鼎神情憔悴。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎神情憔悴。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659396111536128184793.jpeg/ezwPhMjL8sRvbYLLWVlqCjRNm1f_3tK6zBqvK_oarys\" alt=\"李家鼎神情憔悴。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎神情憔悴。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123659392965677056253907.jpeg/irsxJK6yEUXNIpquvLSuwS5frEq9NCtDTHISE3pyEhM\" alt=\"暴瘦成紙片人。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>暴瘦成紙片人。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1667668/org/f4df7f4e01beb48ad0cf9de852c29f5f.JPG/7evTATCW730fpbgnwQtlXmiDO8eIHHwNLOgpIhroKSI\" alt=\"李家鼎2018年的相片。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>李家鼎2018年的相片。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T09:18:56.540157+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":275,"images":7,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}